==Example tree runs==
Start out at the [[Grand Exchange]] and buy all of the saplings, payments and teleports needed.

In the first run, the player will have to rake all of the patches. In subsequent runs, this is only necessary if a [[Farming#Growth cycles|growth cycle]] happens in between removing the tree and planting a new one. It is recommended to leave a rake at a [[Tool Leprechaun]] in case this happens.

===Example low-level tree run===
